{"tid":1038733,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"(Whatsapp)大更新! 第五年既員工折扣交換谷","createTime":"2019-02-27T01:44:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T01:52:14.000Z","uid":75218,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3843850808e252c4792869192c390962ce25f718","tid":1038733,"uid":75218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:44:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">大家好,細佬係員工折扣谷既搞手. 最近將員工折扣大更新左一次,以後大家交換折扣會更方便,個人資料會更受保護,亦都避免左連絡人同實際提供既折扣唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n更新如下:<br />\n1. 將5個折扣谷精簡為2個<br />\n2.更新所有人現有折扣,更準確提供折扣 (因為好多part time sales 已經唔同曬工作)<br />\n3. 會有折扣表 提供俾大家參考 (但不包括<span style=\"color: orange;\">提供折扣者</span><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">任何資料</span></strong>)<br />\n<br />\n申請者只需要填左以下表格,ADMIN就會定期加你入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1EGqy3eDko4JzJ5XpSp3X9_DzsOrfoHgIAJ9_bvmlfM0/edit#response=ACYDBNjFKNTx9l80C5qolQnNRDVeu_45s13u_ndE8QelN5hDc8gw7B2Udw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1EGqy3eDko4JzJ5XpSp3X9_DzsOrfoHgIAJ9_bvmlfM0%2Fedit%23response%3DACYDBNjFKNTx9l80C5qolQnNRDVeu_45s13u_ndE8QelN5hDc8gw7B2Udw&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6TYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=aa826893\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1EGqy3eDko4JzJ5XpSp3X9_DzsOrfoHgIAJ9_bvmlfM0/edit#response=ACYDBNjFKNTx9l80C5qolQnNRDVeu_45s13u_ndE8QelN5hDc8gw7B2Udw</a><br />\n<br />\n謝謝有參與過既人5年黎一直既支持呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da84cdd26ca725162cb05232dabdd84bf92003c","tid":1038733,"uid":75218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T06:17:03.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"cbc6965df07e83c0e80f44403eab2608708c88a7","tid":1038733,"uid":75218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"